creditline: Gift of Dr. Gabriel P. and Mrs. Yvonne M.L. Weisberg
description: display of molded plaster figures and busts with prices; small busts of composers in foreground, with their signatures molded into the front of each base; plaster figure of kneeling young woman at left; three troll-like abstracted darker figures at center right, two playing guitars and a seated woman; two plaster Chinese horses in background, ULQ; Ionic column behind figure of kneeling young woman
signed: on back of mount, in black ink: [Eve Sonneman / \"Los Angeles, 1967\"]
title: Los Angeles
